來吧，一起喝一杯。
Come on. Let's go get a drink.

166
00:17:15,549 --> 00:17:18,170
可以，但是只能一會兒。
um, yeah, OK,
but I've only got a few minutes.

167
00:17:18,301 --> 00:17:20,757
-哦，別這樣…
-已經是最後的準備工作。
- Oh, great...
- It's a last-minute thing.

168
00:17:20,887 --> 00:17:23,971
今晚我們在Buffalo做一次演唱會。
The band got this gig in Buffalo
and we start tonight.

169
00:17:24,099 --> 00:17:26,424
下次別在報紙上登廣告了，行嗎？
Next time don't put
an ad in the paper, OK?

170
00:17:26,559 --> 00:17:29,726
蘇珊，我每週都在找你。
Susan, I've been looking for you
for weeks!

171
00:17:29,754 --> 00:17:31,747
陪我去Buffalo吧？
Come to Buffalo with me?

172
00:17:31,757 --> 00:17:33,714
嗯，你可是在工作。
uh-uh, you'll be working.

173
00:17:33,739 --> 00:17:36,195
-無聊的工作
-陪我去吧。
- (Susan) It's boring.
- Come to Buffalo.

174
00:17:36,226 --> 00:17:39,558
我不會讓你閒著無聊的。
(Jim) I'll find some trouble
for you to get into.

175
00:17:39,687 --> 00:17:41,727
我現在已經沒閒心了。
I've had enough trouble already.

176
00:17:45,026 --> 00:17:47,018
你…你和這人睡過？
You... you were with this guy?

177
00:17:47,152 --> 00:17:49,110
我離開時他還活著。
He was breathing when I left.

178
00:17:49,238 --> 00:17:53,188
嗨，你們美女和野獸兩位，
我可不想在橋上出事，快走！
Hey! Beauty and the Beast,
we'll hit traffic on the bridge. Let's fly!

179
00:17:53,325 --> 00:17:54,950
《生之欲》
(# "Lust For Life" by lggy Pop on radio)

180
00:17:55,077 --> 00:17:57,116
我不能就這樣離開你。
I don't like leaving you like this.

181
00:17:57,245 --> 00:18:00,781
-我能照顧好自己。
-好吧。
- I can take care of myself.
- I know.

182
00:18:00,916 --> 00:18:03,454
這樣，我給你一個電話…
Look, I'll give you a number. uh...

183
00:18:04,252 --> 00:18:06,292
有筆嗎？
You got a pen?

184
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:10,959
好了，這是我朋友迪茲的電話。
All right, this is the number
of my friend Dez.

185
00:18:11,093 --> 00:18:13,131
他人不錯…
He's a great guy...

186
00:18:13,261 --> 00:18:17,129
…如果你有困難了就打給他，他知道怎麼聯繫我。
...and if you really get in a jam, call him.
He'll know how to reach me.

187
00:18:17,265 --> 00:18:21,179
-他有錢嗎？
-別想了，他知道你是什麼人。
- Has he got any money?
- Forget it! He knows all about you.

188
00:18:24,189 --> 00:18:27,273
Johnny Yen又來了，
# Here comes Johnny Yen again

189
00:18:28,150 --> 00:18:30,309
帶著酒和毒品，
# With the liquor and drugs

190
00:18:30,445 --> 00:18:32,651
還有絞肉機
# And the flesh machine

191
00:18:32,780 --> 00:18:34,820
別尋刺激了，好嗎？
No more dead bodies, OK?

192
00:18:34,949 --> 00:18:36,988
我要看看我能幹出什麼來。
I'll see what I can do.

193
00:18:37,910 --> 00:18:40,235
下次我回來還在這裡見面。
Be here next time when I get back.

194
00:18:42,873 --> 00:18:47,535
自從上當後我就沒有好轉…
# And I been hurtin'
since I bought the gimmick...

195
00:19:21,494 --> 00:19:23,534
來吧，寶貝！
Come on, baby!

196
00:19:23,662 --> 00:19:26,154
注意看啊！
(vendor) Check it out!

197
00:19:30,378 --> 00:19:33,912
嗨，寶貝，這太陽鏡專為你準備的。
Hey, baby, I got
a pair of sunglasses just for you!

198
00:19:35,883 --> 00:19:37,923
這帽子再適合你不過了。
This hat'll look great on you, baby.

199
00:19:38,052 --> 00:19:40,543
照照鏡子，好看吧？
Take a look in the mirror.
Beautiful, right?

200
00:19:40,679 --> 00:19:42,802
十美元，便宜吧，十美元。
$10 for the set, all right? Ten bucks.

201
00:19:44,641 --> 00:19:46,930
你買嗎？你哪裡走？
You gonna buy?
Hey, where you goin', babe?

202
00:19:47,061 --> 00:19:49,551
站住！你拿了我的帽子知道嗎？
Yo! Come back!
What are you doin' with my hat?

203
00:19:49,688 --> 00:19:52,095
還給我眼鏡，怎麼回事啊？
Give me my glasses, babe!
What's the matter?

204
00:19:52,232 --> 00:19:54,557
-哦，天，怎麼會這樣！
-對不起。
- Oh, man! I don't believe it!
- I'm sorry.

205
00:19:54,692 --> 00:19:56,732
你在幹什麼？
What are you doin'?

206
00:19:56,862 --> 00:19:59,233
-對不起。
-說句對不起就完了？
- I'm sorry.
- What do you mean, "sorry"? Hey!

207
00:19:59,364 --> 00:20:00,609
抱歉！
Sorry!

208
00:20:22,345 --> 00:20:25,844
《尊嚴》
(# "Respect" by Aretha Franklin
playing in shop)

209
00:20:49,621 --> 00:20:51,448
我不想繼續你的錯誤
# I ain't gonna do you wrong

210
00:20:51,914 --> 00:20:53,907
當你離開
# While you're gone

211
00:20:54,042 --> 00:20:56,082
我不想繼續你的錯誤
# Ain't gonna do you wrong

212
00:20:56,669 --> 00:20:58,163
因為我不想
# Cos I don't wanna

213
00:20:58,296 --> 00:21:00,087
就是你回家時當我問起…
# All I'm askin'

214
00:21:00,215 --> 00:21:03,169
…那一點點尊嚴
# Is for a little respect
when you come home

215
00:21:03,301 --> 00:21:06,053
親愛的，當你回家
# Baby, when you get home

216
00:21:09,723 --> 00:21:11,966
我考慮給你
# I'm about to give you

217
00:21:12,392 --> 00:21:14,635
所有的錢
# All of my money

218
00:21:14,770 --> 00:21:16,846
# And all I'm askin'...

219
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:19,767
給我個面子吧，不要穿出去。
Do me a favour, baby.
Stay on the carpet, OK?

220
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:22,438
-挺好看的，是吧？
-是。
- They're great, aren't they?
- I know.

221
00:21:23,153 --> 00:21:25,193
我想要了，但是65美元的價錢有點…
I gotta have 'em, but 65 bucks...

222
00:21:25,322 --> 00:21:27,445
-那是定價。
-別管定價。
- That is the price.
- Forget it.

223
00:21:27,574 --> 00:21:31,359
-我喜歡你這夾克。
-這是Jimi Hendrix（搖滾明星）的。
- I like the jacket.
- It used to belong to Jimi Hendrix.

224
00:21:31,494 --> 00:21:35,077
但我願意用夾克來換靴子。
But I bet he'd love it
if I swapped it for the boots.

225
00:21:35,957 --> 00:21:37,997
成交。
Deal.

226
00:21:46,843 --> 00:21:49,050
# Ooo, your kiss is

227
00:21:49,178 --> 00:21:50,672
# Sweeter than honey

228
00:21:52,431 --> 00:21:53,463
# And guess what?

229
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:55,841
# So is my money...

230
00:22:08,196 --> 00:22:10,023
很招人喜歡，是吧？
Gorgeous, isn't it?

231
00:22:10,157 --> 00:22:12,197
它曾經可是貓王的。
It used to belong to Elvis Presley.

232
00:22:12,326 --> 00:22:14,995
-試一試嗎？
-行。
- Wanna try it on?
- All right.

233
00:22:15,912 --> 00:22:18,238
# Oh, a little respect

234
00:22:20,125 --> 00:22:22,284
# Oh, hey! A little respect...

235
00:22:58,996 --> 00:23:01,237
我們從雞蛋開始
(TV) We start off with the eggs.

236
00:23:02,166 --> 00:23:04,205
兩個兩個打，動作要快
These go very fast done two by two.

237
00:23:04,334 --> 00:23:06,374
你可以在早晨做
And this you can do in the morning...

238
00:23:07,295 --> 00:23:09,585
然後準備開始做菜。
...and get it all ready for baking.

239
00:23:09,715 --> 00:23:12,420
我會用新方法來做。
I'm gonna bake it and then unmould it.

240
00:23:13,635 --> 00:23:15,675
這有六個雞蛋了。
There are your six eggs.

241
00:23:17,806 --> 00:23:21,934
然後用打蛋器攪拌…
Those get beaten up a little bit
and then in goes...

242
00:23:22,060 --> 00:23:24,017
嗨，羅伯塔
Hello, Roberta.

243
00:23:24,146 --> 00:23:26,102
嗨，朱莉婭
Hello, Julia.

244
00:23:26,230 --> 00:23:28,687
抱歉，主婦們，我不能在家吃晚飯。
Sorry, girls. I can't stay for dinner.

245
00:23:28,817 --> 00:23:31,604
西德的人訂了1500個浴盆
Some guy from West Germany's
got 1500 tubs...

246
00:23:31,736 --> 00:23:33,728
他為人傳統
...he can't get through customs.

247
00:23:33,863 --> 00:23:35,903
我得在鎮上陪他吃飯。
I gotta go have dinner with him in town.

248
00:23:36,032 --> 00:23:38,605
就這一次，我抱歉，你能理解嗎？
It just happened.
I'm sorry. You forgive me?

249
00:23:40,787 --> 00:23:42,826
看起來挺有意思的。
Looks interesting too.

250
00:23:43,707 --> 00:23:46,624
-選好了收音機了嗎？
-收音機？
- Get a good deal on the radio?
- Radio?

251
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:50,535
-汽車上的。你去城裡幹嘛去了？
-哦，對了，收音機。
- Car radio. You just came from the city.
- Oh, my God, the radio.

252
00:23:51,505 --> 00:23:53,545
-你忘了？
-不是。
- You forgot the radio?
- No!

253
00:23:54,258 --> 00:23:56,297
嗯，對，是，我忘了。
um... Yeah, right, I guess I did.

254
00:23:56,427 --> 00:23:59,428
你可以說你不吃晚飯了，而我卻忙的不可開交。
You could have said
you didn't want dinner. I had to rush!

255
00:23:59,555 --> 00:24:01,547
你忙什麼了？你說你什麼地方都沒去。
You said you didn't go anywhere.

256
00:24:01,681 --> 00:24:03,473
你穿的是什麼？
What are you wearing?

257
00:24:04,559 --> 00:24:07,809
夾克。曾經是Jimi Hendrix的夾克。
A jacket.
It used to belong to Jimi Hendrix.

258
00:24:09,397 --> 00:24:11,722
你買了一個穿過的夾克？
怎麼，我們是窮人嗎？
You bought a used jacket?
What, are we poor?

259
00:24:11,858 --> 00:24:13,898
你這是怎麼啦？
What's going on here?

260
00:24:19,866 --> 00:24:22,238
羅伯塔，我必須要去了。
Roberta, I gotta run! I'm late.

261
00:24:22,368 --> 00:24:24,527
我們晚些再談吧。
We'll talk later, all right?

262
00:24:24,663 --> 00:24:26,868
晚些談。
All right, we'll talk later?

263
00:24:30,918 --> 00:24:32,958
Jimi Hendrix,是嗎？
Jimi Hendrix, huh?

264
00:24:42,513 --> 00:24:44,552
落地聲
(clattering)

265
00:24:51,521 --> 00:24:53,561
電視聲
(TV continues)

266
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:04,495
警方尋找神秘女人

267
00:25:25,805 --> 00:25:27,845
你賣了？
You sold it?

268
00:25:28,808 --> 00:25:32,177
我落下了開儲物櫃的鑰匙！
I had a key that was important.
I got my shit inside a locker.

269
00:25:32,312 --> 00:25:35,846
-我賣了。
-我留下名字和電話。
- I sold it!
- I'll leave you my name and number.

270
00:26:03,175 --> 00:26:05,214
動作好快，陌生人！
Good goin', stranger.

271
00:26:06,344 --> 00:26:08,383
什麼他媽的陌生人？
Well, what fuckin' stranger?!

272
00:26:08,513 --> 00:26:11,383
大型通鋪。這意味著尿褲子。
Festival seating. That means Portosans.

273
00:26:11,516 --> 00:26:15,845
尿褲子就是站著撒尿，我不想站著撒尿。
Portosans means pissing with flies.
I'm not gonna piss with flies.

274
00:26:15,978 --> 00:26:19,514
你們男人可以尿在瓶子裡。
這算什麼？木房子？
You guys can piss in bottles.
What the hell is this? Woodstock?

275
00:26:37,749 --> 00:26:39,789
電話聲
(phone rings)

276
00:26:43,171 --> 00:26:45,413
-放映員
-迪茲，是我，吉姆。
- Projection.
- Dez, it's me. Jim.

277
00:26:45,549 --> 00:26:47,376
等一會兒。
Hold on a second.

278
00:26:50,345 --> 00:26:52,384
哦，我的天啊。
Jesus Christ!

279
00:26:52,514 --> 00:26:56,463
我在Buffalo脫不了身，請你幫個忙，
是關於蘇珊的。
I'm stuck in Buffalo and I need a favour.
It's about Susan.

280
00:26:56,601 --> 00:27:02,390
是這樣，她在大西洋城遇到的一個傢伙
被人從旅店的窗戶上扔了出去。
See, now some guy she met in Atlantic
City got pushed out of a hotel window.

281
00:27:02,523 --> 00:27:04,765
這裡太亂了，我沒聽見。
This sounds wild. I'm sorry I missed it.

282
00:27:04,901 --> 00:27:06,940
迪茲，我沒開玩笑。
This is serious, Dez.

283
00:27:07,069 --> 00:27:11,482
現在，一個署名陌生人的傢伙登出啟事
要在巴特利公園見她
And now some guy's run an ad to meet
her in Battery Park, signed "a stranger".

284
00:27:11,615 --> 00:27:15,743
這有點怪了，你能不能
It sounds weird.
Could you just go down there...

285
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:17,743
去看一下她安全嗎？
...and make sure she's OK?

286
00:27:17,872 --> 00:27:21,869
吉姆，維多利亞昨晚剛甩了我，
我心情糟透了。
Jim, Victoria split on me last night.
I'm in a shitty mood.

287
00:27:22,001 --> 00:27:24,871
我沒法立刻就變成你的童子軍。
I'm not in the mood for being a boy scout
right now.

288
00:27:25,004 --> 00:27:27,245
拜託了，迪茲，就耽誤你半個小時。
Come on, Dez.
It'll take you half an hour.

289
00:27:27,380 --> 00:27:30,964
-好了沒有？
-馬上就好，一秒鐘就好。
- (man) Come on!
- Give me a chance here. One second.

290
00:27:31,093 --> 00:27:32,671
起哄聲
(booing)

291
00:27:32,803 --> 00:27:36,503
-她在四點去見他。
-四點？那可要差不多一個小時！
- She's got to meet him at 4 o'clock.
- That's in less than an hour!

292
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:38,847
吉姆，我可是有工作的人！
Jim, I got a job here, you know!

293
00:27:38,975 --> 00:27:41,015
我求你了。
This one favour.

294
00:27:41,144 --> 00:27:43,599
即使我能找到人替我
Even if I could get someone
to fill in for me,...

295
00:27:43,730 --> 00:27:45,889
可我連她長得什麼樣都不知道。
...I don't even know what she looks like.

296
00:27:46,024 --> 00:27:48,063
聽著，你不會找不到她的。
Look, you can't miss her.

297
00:27:48,192 --> 00:27:51,776
她很好看，金髮，還有，中等身材
She's incredibly pretty,
blonde hair, uh... medium height.

298
00:27:51,905 --> 00:27:54,277
還有她穿著綠色的，上面畫著金色的…
And she's got this green and gold jacket...

299
00:27:54,407 --> 00:27:58,654
一個錐形，一隻眼睛在上面，就像鈔票上那樣。
（共濟會標誌）你肯定能找到她。
...with a pyramid with an eye on top
like a dollar bill. You can't miss it.

300
00:27:58,786 --> 00:28:03,033
-好吧，你要請我吃飯啊。
-行，多謝，我一定請你。
- All right, you owe me one.
- Great. Thanks, Dez, I appreciate it.

301
00:28:03,165 --> 00:28:05,205
好的，再見。
OK, yeah. Bye.

302
00:28:06,419 --> 00:28:08,458
我一輩子都在紐約。
I lived in New York all my life.

303
00:28:08,587 --> 00:28:11,754
我們老去中餐館，意餐館
We used to have Chinese restaurants,
ltalian restaurants.

304
00:28:11,882 --> 00:28:15,251
現在你去吃壽司。所有人都吃壽司。
Now you have these sushi restaurants.
Everyone goes for sushi.

305
00:28:15,386 --> 00:28:17,425
壽司，我討厭這東西。
Sushi... I hate the stuff.

306
00:28:17,554 --> 00:28:20,306
我跟你說，儘管我有一天我買了一些，
Although, I tell you,
I had some the other day.

307
00:28:20,432 --> 00:28:24,181
回家做了，還不錯的，味道像魚。
I took it home, I cooked it, it wasn't bad.
It tasted like fish.

308
00:28:24,311 --> 00:28:26,350
鼓聲
(drumming)

309
00:28:51,128 --> 00:28:53,168
9塊2.
$9.20.

310
00:28:55,466 --> 00:28:57,506
給，不用找了。
Here, keep the change.

311
00:28:57,635 --> 00:29:00,802
哇，這是什麼？嗨，女士！
Whoa! Hey! What is that? Hey, lady!

312
00:29:00,930 --> 00:29:02,969
嗨，女士！
Hey! Hey, lady!

313
00:29:03,098 --> 00:29:05,056
這算什麼？
What is this?

314
00:29:05,184 --> 00:29:07,093
靠，刁民！
Oh, that's cute!

315
00:29:11,815 --> 00:29:13,855
嗨
Hi.

316
00:29:15,903 --> 00:29:18,524
我以前好像見過你。
You look like I've seen you
somewhere before.

317
00:29:18,656 --> 00:29:21,526
-不，我想不是。
-我想是。
- No, I don't think so.
- Yeah, I think so.

318
00:29:24,035 --> 00:29:27,783
-你現在在做什麼事情嗎？
-我在等人。
- You doin' anything right now?
- I'm waiting for someone.

319
00:29:38,508 --> 00:29:41,711
-跟我走，小姐。
-你不明白，我必須去見一個人。
- Come with me, miss.
- I have to meet someone.

320
00:29:41,844 --> 00:29:44,798
-我們談談出租車裡的事情。
-她那裡有我所有的東西。
- We'll talk about it in the car.
- She's got all my stuff.

321
00:29:44,931 --> 00:29:47,682
她會給你他媽的打車費。
She'll give you the goddamn cab fare!

322
00:29:49,018 --> 00:29:52,718
我也不想這樣，可我也得生活。
(driver) I don't need this aggravation.
I work for a living.

323
00:29:52,855 --> 00:29:54,894
想吃霸王餐，我知道法律。
Theft of services. I know the law.

