你真噁心，跟你爸一樣。怪不得羅伯塔離開你。
You're disgusting. You're just like Daddy!
No wonder Roberta left you.

488
00:43:12,796 --> 00:43:14,836
你說夠了嗎！
Would you stop saying that!

489
00:43:14,965 --> 00:43:17,004
-加裡
-賴瑞
- Gary...
- Larry!

490
00:43:17,133 --> 00:43:19,802
看著不錯。有羅伯塔的消息嗎？
That looks great.
Any word from Roberta yet?

491
00:43:19,927 --> 00:43:21,636
這麼快就搞上了，萊斯莉。
Fast work, Les.

492
00:43:21,763 --> 00:43:23,803
哦，這裡還有一些雞肉。
Oh, let's have some chicken.

493
00:43:23,932 --> 00:43:25,971
賴瑞，那是明天吃的。
The chicken is for tomorrow. Larry!

494
00:43:26,100 --> 00:43:28,010
警察怎麼說？
What did the police say?

495
00:43:28,144 --> 00:43:30,813
出了這麼大的事你們還吃東西！
I can't believe
you're eating during a crisis!

496
00:43:30,939 --> 00:43:32,349
我們夠緊張的了，你還要怎麼樣？
We're nervous!

497
00:43:32,482 --> 00:43:35,269
那你們應該像個正常人那樣去打鎮定劑！
Then take a Valium like a normal person!

498
00:43:40,489 --> 00:43:42,529
她有一口好牙。
She has great teeth.

499
00:43:43,409 --> 00:43:46,659
這就是我為什麼出現在巴特利公園
(Dez)
That's why I showed up at Battery Park.

500
00:43:47,704 --> 00:43:51,999
吉姆說你的一個朋友摔死在
大西洋城的旅館外邊。
Jim said a friend of yours got killed
outside your hotel in Atlantic City.

501
00:43:52,125 --> 00:43:54,165
他擔心壞了。
He was pretty worried.

502
00:43:54,294 --> 00:43:56,334
摔了？
Killed?

503
00:43:56,463 --> 00:43:58,337
殺死了？
Dead?

504
00:43:58,465 --> 00:44:02,048
這也是你的興趣之一，是嗎，蘇珊？
Sort of goes with the territory,
doesn't it, Susan?

505
00:44:04,513 --> 00:44:06,553
也許我知道是誰幹的。
Maybe I know who did it.

506
00:44:08,224 --> 00:44:10,264
我希望我能想起來。
I wish I could remember.

507
00:44:12,479 --> 00:44:14,518
也許就是你殺的。
Maybe you were the killer.

508
00:44:15,357 --> 00:44:17,396
不可能。
No! (laughs)

509
00:44:22,739 --> 00:44:25,693
我想我要躺一會兒
I should probably lay low for while, huh?

510
00:44:26,284 --> 00:44:28,323
好主意。
It might be a wise idea.

511
00:44:30,121 --> 00:44:33,075
你不知道在碼頭的那個人是誰？
You don't know
who the guy at the quay was?

512
00:44:35,626 --> 00:44:37,665
也許是被你拋棄的情人
Maybe a jilted lover?

513
00:44:41,382 --> 00:44:43,422
肯定不是。
I don't think so.

514
00:44:46,262 --> 00:44:48,301
也有可能。
Maybe he was.

515
00:44:49,181 --> 00:44:51,304
你可知道
You know somethin'?

516
00:44:51,433 --> 00:44:54,054
你不完全是我所想的那樣。
You are not at all what I expected.

517
00:44:55,604 --> 00:44:58,142
你也不全是我想的那樣。
You're not quite what I expected either.

518
00:45:00,191 --> 00:45:02,231
薩克斯
(sax ophone)

519
00:45:19,585 --> 00:45:22,622
我怎麼認識的吉姆？我是說…
Just how did I meet Jim? I mean, how...

520
00:45:23,380 --> 00:45:25,420
我怎麼遇到他的？
How did I meet him?

521
00:45:25,550 --> 00:45:27,588
也許這個有幫助。
Maybe it would help.

522
00:45:27,718 --> 00:45:30,174
我想是在那個咖啡店裡。
I think it was at some coffee shop.

523
00:45:31,472 --> 00:45:33,511
那是你工作的第一天，
It was your first day at work.

524
00:45:33,640 --> 00:45:35,680
吉姆大搖大擺的進來。
Jim waltzed in.

525
00:45:35,809 --> 00:45:38,894
你給他帶來吃的，然後把帳單撕了。
You brought his food over
and you ripped up the check.

526
00:45:40,606 --> 00:45:43,891
他個高嗎？我說的是吉姆。
Is he tall? I mean Jim.

527
00:45:44,902 --> 00:45:47,143
中等個頭吧。
He's about medium.

528
00:45:48,655 --> 00:45:50,695
哪種身材？
Is he sort of thin?

529
00:45:52,117 --> 00:45:54,156
哪種，哪種，呃…
Sort of. Sort of, um...

530
00:45:55,078 --> 00:45:57,070
跟我差不多。
...my build.

531
00:46:00,750 --> 00:46:02,873
眼睛是什麼顏色的？
What colour eyes does he have?

532
00:46:07,090 --> 00:46:08,998
藍的。
Blue.

533
00:46:09,133 --> 00:46:11,173
跟你一樣？
Like yours?

534
00:46:18,058 --> 00:46:20,051
抱歉，抱歉。
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

535
00:46:20,186 --> 00:46:22,225
抱歉。
(Roberta whispers) Sorry.

536
00:46:23,605 --> 00:46:26,311
我不知道怎麼回事，只是…
I don't know what happened. I just...

537
00:46:27,109 --> 00:46:28,603
不好意思。
Sorry.

538
00:46:33,198 --> 00:46:35,237
雷聲
(thunder rumbles)

539
00:47:34,716 --> 00:47:36,756
哼哼
(groans)

540
00:47:44,684 --> 00:47:46,724
過來。
Come on.

541
00:48:08,958 --> 00:48:10,997
迪茲
(whispers) Dez!

542
00:48:11,836 --> 00:48:13,874
迪茲
Dez...

543
00:48:19,385 --> 00:48:21,424
和我一起吃早餐嗎？
Wanna go out to breakfast with me?

544
00:48:22,388 --> 00:48:24,427
早餐
Breakfast?

545
00:48:26,642 --> 00:48:29,559
你怎麼了？穿的有點噁心。
What have you got on?
Some sort of disguise?

546
00:48:29,686 --> 00:48:32,936
-你不喜歡？
-不，只是，呃…
- You don't like it?
- No, it's, uh...

547
00:48:33,064 --> 00:48:35,851
還是迷人的。
...sort of charming.

548
00:48:37,194 --> 00:48:38,936
我請客。
It's my treat.

549
00:48:40,113 --> 00:48:42,152
你要幹嘛？搶銀行？
What did you do? Rob a bank?

550
00:48:42,281 --> 00:48:45,199
我不知道，也許吧。
I don't know. Maybe.

551
00:48:46,953 --> 00:48:48,827
你要到哪裡去？
Where do you wanna go?

552
00:48:48,954 --> 00:48:51,196
看，我在手提箱找到這個。
See, I found this in the suitcase.

553
00:48:52,792 --> 00:48:54,832
Gunny的咖啡店？我知道這地方。
Gunny's Coffee Shop? I know the place.

554
00:48:54,960 --> 00:48:57,000
它在中央大街附近。
It's over on Center Street.

555
00:48:57,129 --> 00:48:59,916
也許我就是在那兒遇見吉姆的。
Maybe that's the place where I met Jim.

556
00:49:00,508 --> 00:49:01,836
-然後？
-然後…
- So?
- So...

557
00:49:01,968 --> 00:49:06,380
然後我們就去那裡
看看是否有人認識我。
So we go there
and see if anybody remembers me.

558
00:49:06,514 --> 00:49:09,763
看得怎麼樣，有熟悉的嗎？
So what do you think?
Anyone look familiar?

559
00:49:11,226 --> 00:49:13,468
還沒有。
No. Not yet.

560
00:49:22,237 --> 00:49:25,072
我在手提箱裡找到這個，你聽說過嗎？
I found this in the suitcase.
You ever hear of it?

561
00:49:25,198 --> 00:49:28,732
魔術俱樂部？是的，在百老匯附近。
The Magic Club? Yeah.
That's that place over on Broadway.

562
00:49:28,868 --> 00:49:30,196
怎麼了？
Why?

563
00:49:30,328 --> 00:49:33,033
我想我應該去那，看看有沒有熟人。
I thought I'd go there
and see if I remember anyone.

564
00:49:33,164 --> 00:49:35,869
-你知道你要點什麼嗎？
-當然。
- You know what you're having?
- Sure.

565
00:49:36,000 --> 00:49:38,040
你要點什麼？
What are you having?

566
00:49:38,169 --> 00:49:40,209
嗯，是你請客，對吧？
Well, it's your treat, right?

567
00:49:40,338 --> 00:49:42,330
是的，我付賬。
(giggles) Yeah, I got money.

568
00:49:42,465 --> 00:49:44,541
我要點…藍莓點心。
I'm gonna have... blueberry blintzes.

569
00:49:44,676 --> 00:49:46,714
很好，我也要那個。
I'll have that too. That sounds good.

570
00:49:46,844 --> 00:49:48,884
你要點什麼？
What can I get you?

571
00:49:49,013 --> 00:49:51,385
呃，一杯咖啡。
Yes, I would like a... coffee...

572
00:49:52,141 --> 00:49:54,513
還有…甜圈餅
...and a, uh... doughnut.

573
00:49:54,643 --> 00:49:58,890
小姐，如果你有空了，就給我們上吃的吧。
Miss! When you get a chance,
could you take our order?

574
00:49:59,023 --> 00:50:00,980
給你可以，她可不行。
You can stay. She's gotta go.

575
00:50:01,107 --> 00:50:03,646
Mick，那個穿夾克的瘋子女孩來了。
Mick, it's that crazy girl with the jacket.

576
00:50:03,777 --> 00:50:05,816
-你，滾！
-你認識我？
- You, out!
- You know me?!

577
00:50:05,946 --> 00:50:08,069
對，別想在這兒吃霸王餐。
Yeah. You won't get a free meal here.

578
00:50:08,198 --> 00:50:11,567
-我有錢，我可以付款。
-我不要你的錢，滾出去。
- I got money, I can pay.
- I don't want your money. Get out.

579
00:50:11,701 --> 00:50:14,406
-我們有錢，怎麼了？
-想想你自己的事吧。
- We got money. What is it?
- Mind your own business.

580
00:50:14,537 --> 00:50:17,289
-這就是我的事，等一下。
-過來，出去。
- This is my business, wait a minute!
- Come on, out!

581
00:50:17,415 --> 00:50:20,119
-嘿，我和他一起的。
-出去，出去。
- Hey, I'm with her.
- Come on, come on.

582
00:50:21,627 --> 00:50:24,000
你幸運去吧，我沒向你逼帳！
You're lucky I don't press charges!

583
00:50:24,130 --> 00:50:25,755
迪茲。
Dez.

584
00:50:25,882 --> 00:50:28,455
你怎麼樣，還好吧？太對不起了。
Are you OK? Are you all right? I'm sorry!

585
00:50:28,593 --> 00:50:30,668
我說的第一條規則就是別給我找事。
Rule number one was no drama.

586
00:50:30,803 --> 00:50:33,970
-記得嗎？
-是的，我知道，抱歉。
- Remember?
- Yes. I know. I'm sorry.

587
00:50:35,474 --> 00:50:37,266
我們走吧。
Let's get out of here.

588
00:50:37,393 --> 00:50:38,971
不好意思。
I'm sorry.

589
00:50:53,158 --> 00:50:55,235
爭吵聲
(man and woman arguing)

590
00:50:55,368 --> 00:50:58,404
你從來不讓我戴眼鏡。
(woman)
You won't even let me wear my glasses!

591
00:50:58,538 --> 00:51:01,954
回去賣T椊去吧，你被解雇了！
(man) Go back to selling T-shirts!
You're fired!

592
00:51:02,084 --> 00:51:05,250
不對，你錯了，藍，是我辭職不幹了。
(shouts) No, you don't, lan, because I quit!

593
00:51:07,380 --> 00:51:09,919
嘿，別在梯子下面！
(Susan) Hey! Not under the ladder!

594
00:51:12,510 --> 00:51:16,638
我的命運絕不可能比這兒更糟糕的了。
敗類人渣！
My luck can't get much worse anyway.
Miserable scumbags!

595
00:51:17,390 --> 00:51:19,846
也許我應該在床上教訓他。
Maybe I should've slept with him.

596
00:51:19,976 --> 00:51:22,763
姐們，有個巫婆偷了我的衣服…
Man, some witch steals my clothes,...

597
00:51:22,896 --> 00:51:27,142
…米克爾被人從旅店窗戶扔了出去，
現在你又被炒了。
...Meeker gets pushed out a hotel window
and now you get fired.

598
00:51:27,275 --> 00:51:31,568
不太糟，但是壞運氣好像抓著你不放。
No offence, but bad luck really seems
to be following you around.

599
00:51:34,240 --> 00:51:37,573
我們現在都清閒了，一起去看個電影吧。
We're both free now.
Let's just go to the movies.

600
00:51:37,702 --> 00:51:39,740
兩場連映的？
A double feature?

601
00:51:39,870 --> 00:51:41,910
來吧。
Come on!

602
00:51:43,915 --> 00:51:46,668
如果你請我吃爆米花的話，電影票就我買了。
I'll pay for the movie
if you pay for the popcorn.

603
00:51:46,794 --> 00:51:48,371
可以，但是，爆米花多少錢？
OK, but listen. How much is popcorn?

604
00:51:48,503 --> 00:51:50,543
-2.50
-行。
- 2.50
- OK.

605
00:51:52,633 --> 00:51:54,672
笑
(giggling)

606
00:52:02,642 --> 00:52:04,681
就是這地方。
This must be the place.

607
00:52:04,811 --> 00:52:07,728
司機，靠邊停吧，就是這兒。
Sir, could you pull over, please?
This is it.

608
00:52:09,273 --> 00:52:11,313
真是不好意思。
I'm sorry about what happened.

609
00:52:12,109 --> 00:52:14,565
-你沒有生氣吧？
-沒。
- Are you sure you're not angry?
- Yeah.

610
00:52:15,404 --> 00:52:17,444
-真的。
-我沒生氣。
- Really?
- I'm not angry.

611
00:52:18,240 --> 00:52:20,280
你真夠哥們。
OK. You're a real pal.

612
00:52:21,702 --> 00:52:23,741
我會告訴吉姆的。
I'll tell Jim.

613
00:52:24,538 --> 00:52:26,448
-拜
-拜
- Bye!
- Bye.

614
00:52:33,673 --> 00:52:35,711
夠哥們，我會告訴吉姆…
A real pal. I'll tell Jim...

615
00:52:38,426 --> 00:52:40,585
布利克大街電影院
Bleecker Street Cinema.

616
00:52:50,730 --> 00:52:53,185
你只是別再這樣開除誰！
(man)
You just don't fire someone like that!

617
00:52:53,316 --> 00:52:55,392
我上哪裡去找這麼文靜的女孩去？
Who am I gonna find
at such short notice?

618
00:52:55,527 --> 00:52:57,566
拜託，你認識那麼多女孩。
Come on, Ray. You know lots of girls.

619
00:52:57,695 --> 00:53:01,610
-很多女人都在找工作。
-媽，別打擾我。
- (woman) Plenty of women need work.
- (Ray) Ma! Let me take care of this.

620
00:53:01,741 --> 00:53:02,820
你好。
Hello.

621
00:53:02,951 --> 00:53:04,824
你看見外邊的招工告示了？
You saw the sign outside?

622
00:53:04,952 --> 00:53:06,861
你是在找工作？
Are you looking for a job?

623
00:53:08,665 --> 00:53:10,740
是的，我想我是。
Yeah. Yeah, I think I am.

624
00:53:10,874 --> 00:53:13,033
-她還在想她在找工作。
-不。
- She thinks she's looking for a job.
- No!

625
00:53:13,169 --> 00:53:15,790
我是在找工作，是什麼工作？
I am, I am! What kind of job?

626
00:53:15,921 --> 00:53:18,044
進來吧。
Come on in.

627
00:53:18,173 --> 00:53:20,213
這位是雷。
This is Ray.

628
00:53:20,342 --> 00:53:22,381
-您好。
-這位是雷的媽媽，格蕾妲。
- Hello.
- This is Ray's mom, Gilda.

629
00:53:22,511 --> 00:53:23,626
嗨。
Hi.

630
00:53:23,763 --> 00:53:25,386
-這位是哈雷。
-嗨。
- This is Henry.
- Hi.

631
00:53:25,514 --> 00:53:26,889
您好，哈雷。
Hello, Henry.

632
00:53:27,015 --> 00:53:29,055
還有我，藍。
And I'm lan.

633
00:53:31,520 --> 00:53:33,477
收音機
(radio on)

634
00:53:44,116 --> 00:53:46,154
加裡先生，你還好嗎？
Are you OK, Mr Glass?

635
00:53:46,284 --> 00:53:48,657
還行，謝謝你。晚安，Daisy。
Fine, thank you. Good night, Daisy.

636
00:53:48,787 --> 00:53:51,112
我希望加裡夫人沒事。
I hope you get good news
about Mrs Glass.

637
00:53:51,247 --> 00:53:52,243
謝謝。
Thank you.

638
00:53:52,832 --> 00:53:54,824
你拿這個包去哪？
Where did you get this bag?

639
00:53:54,959 --> 00:53:56,999
它是我的，加裡夫人把它給我了。
It's mine. Mrs Glass give it to me.

640
00:53:57,128 --> 00:53:59,167
把包給我，Daisy。
Give me the bag, Daisy.

641
00:53:59,964 --> 00:54:03,214
-Daisy，把包給我。
-對不起，這包是我的。
- Daisy, give me the bag!
- Sorry, you ain't getting this bag.

642
00:54:03,343 --> 00:54:06,508
-請你給我，我要好好的問問你。
-這包是我的。
- Please, I'm asking you nicely.
- You're not getting this.

643
00:54:06,637 --> 00:54:09,093
《笨蛋主持》
(# "Sucker MCs" by Run DMC
on ghetto blaster)

644
00:54:19,024 --> 00:54:23,271
嘿，我說，你們能挪個地方吃東西嗎？
Hey, guys. Could you, uh...
have your picnic somewhere else?

645
00:54:31,452 --> 00:54:33,492
嘿，你們這些人！
Hey, guys!

646
00:54:35,165 --> 00:54:36,540
好吧，
Right...

647
00:54:36,666 --> 00:54:39,121
小心輕放，行吧？
Just try to be careful, all right?

648
00:54:42,463 --> 00:54:45,714
聽著，我不想捲入家庭糾紛，好嗎。
Listen, I don't get involved
in domestic disputes, OK?

649
00:54:45,842 --> 00:54:47,668
不是糾紛。
There's no dispute.

650
00:54:47,802 --> 00:54:50,127
在她沒有失蹤前時，她穿著一件夾克。
She had the jacket on
when she disappeared.

651
00:54:50,263 --> 00:54:53,299
某種原因上講，這對她很不一樣。
It was very special to her
for some reason.

652
00:54:53,433 --> 00:54:55,508
你真的記不起來她了？
Don't you even remember her?

653
00:54:55,643 --> 00:54:57,683
你也記不起來夾克了？
Don't you remember the jacket?

654
00:54:57,812 --> 00:55:02,473
黑色的，上面還有一個金色的像金字塔的圖形
It was black and gold and it had
a sort of a pyramid thing on it...

655
00:55:02,608 --> 00:55:04,351
就像鈔票上的那樣。
...like on a dollar bill.

