是啊，這個與她無關，而與我有關，聽聽這個。
Yeah, well, it's not about her.
It's about me. Listen to this.

994
01:20:06,897 --> 01:20:10,231
他又開始找蘇珊了，她從墨西哥州回來晚了。
"He's looking for Susan again.
She's late returning from Mexico."

995
01:20:10,359 --> 01:20:12,316
這是他第五個啟事了。
"This is his fifth ad."

996
01:20:12,444 --> 01:20:15,778
為什麼他如此強烈的想要見她？
她是誰？
"Why does he want to see her so badly?
Who is she?"

997
01:20:15,906 --> 01:20:18,147
還有我的一張照片。
And there's my picture.

998
01:20:19,076 --> 01:20:22,242
加裡，為什麼你不告訴我她讀了這些啟事呢？
Gary, why didn't you tell me
she read the personals?

999
01:20:22,370 --> 01:20:24,410
我們昨天就可以搞定了。
We could've settled this yesterday.

1000
01:20:24,539 --> 01:20:27,291
她一直都在看這些啟事。我不認為…
She read them all the time. I didn't think...

1001
01:20:27,417 --> 01:20:31,960
嗯，是。幸虧了每一個人，
我才能活下來想做點什麼。
Yeah, well, fortunately for everybody,
I'm here and I'm thinking.

1002
01:20:32,089 --> 01:20:34,127
把車鑰匙給我。
Give me the car keys.

1003
01:20:36,676 --> 01:20:38,799
我會把它完整帶回來的。
I'll bring it right back.

1004
01:20:38,928 --> 01:20:40,506
嘿咻。
Hiya.

1005
01:20:41,264 --> 01:20:44,218
加裡。她拿的是你的汽車鑰匙。
Gary! She is taking the car keys!

1006
01:20:46,394 --> 01:20:49,181
別說了，萊斯莉，行嗎？
Shut up, Leslie. OK?

1007
01:20:50,314 --> 01:20:54,775
日記本。有點偷偷摸摸的感覺。
她是怎麼評論我的？
Diary. That little sneak,
what did she say about me?

1008
01:21:18,425 --> 01:21:21,710
瘋狂尋找
陌生人尋找蘇珊
"Desperately seeking
stranger seeking Susan."

1009
01:21:21,845 --> 01:21:26,092
敬啟者，在星期六晚9點半，百老匯魔術俱樂部見。
"Regarding key. Meet me Saturday night,
Magic Club, Broadway. 9.30pm. Be there."

1010
01:21:26,224 --> 01:21:28,430
-就這些了？
-她會喜歡的。
- Is that it?
- She'll love it.

1011
01:21:28,559 --> 01:21:30,599
去櫃檯付錢。
Pay at the cashier.

1012
01:21:34,649 --> 01:21:37,685
四十歲單身白人男性，
尋找下午的玩伴。
"Single white male, 40,
looking for afternoon playmates."

1013
01:21:37,819 --> 01:21:41,104
就這些了？去櫃檯付錢。
Is that it? Pay at the cashier.

1014
01:21:55,836 --> 01:21:57,663
迪茲…
Dez...

1015
01:21:59,631 --> 01:22:01,671
我不是蘇珊。
I'm not Susan.

1016
01:22:02,801 --> 01:22:05,885
我是家庭主婦，住在紐澤西李堡。
I'm a housewife
and I live in Fort Lee, New Jersey.

1017
01:22:06,763 --> 01:22:09,219
我已經結婚四年了。
I've been married for four years.

1018
01:22:09,350 --> 01:22:11,009
我丈夫加裡…
My husband Gary...

1019
01:22:11,142 --> 01:22:15,306
他做浴盆和浴室的生意。
He sells bathroom spas and saunas.

1020
01:22:20,652 --> 01:22:22,692
你怎麼還是這樣？
You never stop, do you?

1021
01:22:22,820 --> 01:22:25,027
不，這是真的，真的。
No, really! Really!

1022
01:22:25,156 --> 01:22:29,783
這就是我喜歡你的原因，我從不知道你
下一句會說什麼，過來。
That's why I like you. I never know
what you'll say next. Come here.

1023
01:22:33,122 --> 01:22:36,076
-門鎖聲
-迪茲。
- (door lock rattles)
- Dez.

1024
01:22:38,795 --> 01:22:40,834
-那是什麼？
-不知道。
- What is that?
- I dunno.

1025
01:22:43,174 --> 01:22:45,213
有人想進來。
Someone's trying to get in.

1026
01:22:55,393 --> 01:22:57,386
哦，天啊。
Oh, my God.

1027
01:22:57,521 --> 01:22:59,514
哦，是吉姆。
Oh, my God, it's Jim.

1028
01:22:59,647 --> 01:23:01,687
天啊。
Oh, my God.

1029
01:23:04,653 --> 01:23:08,188
吉姆，吉姆。
Jim... Jim. Jim.

1030
01:23:08,656 --> 01:23:13,698
謝天謝地，你嚇壞我了。你覺得怎麼樣，啊？
Thank God. You had me worried.
How you doing, man? Huh? Huh?

1031
01:23:13,828 --> 01:23:16,699
有人打我了，一片黑。
Somebody jumped me. It was dark.

1032
01:23:17,415 --> 01:23:19,574
嗯，呃…
Yeah. uh...

1033
01:23:20,126 --> 01:23:22,165
是我幹的。
It was me.

1034
01:23:22,921 --> 01:23:25,458
我以為你是別人呢。
I thought you were somebody else.

1035
01:23:25,590 --> 01:23:27,629
你以為我是誰？
Who did you think I was?

1036
01:23:29,218 --> 01:23:32,801
有人跟蹤了蘇珊，我想你可能是他。
Somebody's been following Susan.
I thought maybe you were him.

1037
01:23:32,930 --> 01:23:34,887
誰跟蹤她？
Who's following her?

1038
01:23:35,015 --> 01:23:36,759
不知道。
I don't know.

1039
01:23:36,892 --> 01:23:38,684
你知道蘇珊。
You know Susan.

1040
01:23:38,811 --> 01:23:42,262
從她那裡得到一個清楚的答案真是困難。
It's really tough
to get a straight answer out of her.

1041
01:23:44,525 --> 01:23:46,518
她需要我，迪茲。
She needs me, Dez.

1042
01:23:46,651 --> 01:23:48,977
我想或許她準備安頓下來了。
I think maybe she's ready to settle down.

1043
01:23:49,113 --> 01:23:53,573
安頓下來？蘇珊？別扯了，吉姆。
Settle down? Susan? Come on, Jim!

1044
01:23:53,701 --> 01:23:56,785
她從沒有做過什麼安頓的事，
她不是那類人。
She'd never do that.
She's really not the type.

1045
01:23:56,911 --> 01:23:58,904
從什麼時候你這麼瞭解她？
Since when do you know her so well?

1046
01:23:59,039 --> 01:24:03,118
呃，我只是不能看見她安頓下來。
我是說，她太野性了。
Well, I just can't see her settling down.
I mean, she's too wild.

1047
01:24:03,251 --> 01:24:05,577
但是這也是她的魅力。
But that's what's so great about her.

1048
01:24:05,711 --> 01:24:07,289
是這樣嗎？
Is that so?

1049
01:24:07,421 --> 01:24:10,755
我是說，你真的好像對她做了一番檢查。
I mean, you really seem
to have examined this.

1050
01:24:11,468 --> 01:24:14,551
嗯，我們一起度過了一些時間。
Well, we've been spending
some time together.

1051
01:24:17,598 --> 01:24:20,350
可…你在說什麼呀，迪茲？
Just... what are you saying here, Dez?

1052
01:24:20,476 --> 01:24:21,886
啊？
Huh?

1053
01:24:24,355 --> 01:24:26,596
我不想對你胡說八道，吉姆。
I'm not gonna bullshit you, Jim.

1054
01:24:26,732 --> 01:24:29,816
是一件不好出口的事，
我沒說它沒有。
It was a shitty thing to do.
I'm not saying it wasn't.

1055
01:24:30,902 --> 01:24:33,689
但是你自己說她誘人的。
But you yourself said she was irresistible.

1056
01:24:36,033 --> 01:24:38,072
哦，不會吧。
Oh, man.

1057
01:24:38,201 --> 01:24:41,701
你，你為什麼不再打我一下，就像這樣的，
把我結果了？
W-why don't you just hit me again
and, like, finish me off?

1058
01:24:41,830 --> 01:24:43,870
-你看…
-啊？
- Look...
- Huh?!

1059
01:24:43,998 --> 01:24:46,537
別哭喊了。我真的為她而瘋狂…
Don't cry about it.
I'm really crazy about her...

1060
01:24:46,669 --> 01:24:48,660
…而且她也為我而瘋狂。
...and she's really crazy about me.

1061
01:24:48,795 --> 01:24:51,121
-我對不起，
-聽著，我瞭解蘇珊。
- I'm sorry.
- Listen. I know Susan.

1062
01:24:51,255 --> 01:24:53,462
無論她告訴什麼都是胡扯。
Whatever she told you doesn't mean shit.

1063
01:24:53,592 --> 01:24:57,755
她不是認真的，迪茲。我是知道的，
我追了她好幾年了。
She plays with people, Dez. I oughta
know, I've been chasing her for years.

1064
01:24:57,887 --> 01:25:00,259
我認為她跟我是認真的。
I don't think she's playing with me.

1065
01:25:00,389 --> 01:25:02,429
胡說。
Bullshit.

1066
01:25:03,184 --> 01:25:05,058
這樣吧，吉姆。
All right, Jim.

1067
01:25:05,186 --> 01:25:07,226
我們幹嘛不問問她呢？
Why don't we just ask her?

1068
01:25:09,774 --> 01:25:11,185
蘇珊。
Susan!

1069
01:25:11,317 --> 01:25:13,605
蘇…她在這兒？
Su...! You mean she's here?!

1070
01:25:14,987 --> 01:25:16,398
蘇珊。
Susan!

1071
01:25:16,530 --> 01:25:18,986
-到這兒來。
-蘇珊。
- Come on out here.
- Susan...!

1072
01:25:22,578 --> 01:25:24,618
蘇珊。
Susan!

1073
01:25:34,089 --> 01:25:36,129
她走了。
She's gone.

1074
01:25:38,052 --> 01:25:40,008
她就在這兒。
She was here.

1075
01:25:40,136 --> 01:25:42,176
我發誓。
I swear to God.

1076
01:25:42,306 --> 01:25:44,344
水壺鳴響
(kettle whistles)

1077
01:26:34,188 --> 01:26:36,228
迪茲，你在上面嗎？
(Jim) Dez, are you up there?

1078
01:26:37,650 --> 01:26:39,310
怎麼了？
Yeah?

1079
01:26:41,029 --> 01:26:44,113
猜猜怎麼了？
我想她把我倆都耍了。
Guess what, man?
I think she's jerking us both around.

1080
01:26:44,241 --> 01:26:45,865
你什麼意思？
What do you mean?

1081
01:26:45,991 --> 01:26:49,443
你看看吧，這個他媽的陌生人是誰？
Check this out.
I mean, who the hell is this stranger?

1082
01:26:49,579 --> 01:26:50,824
鼓
(drum roll)

1083
01:27:05,427 --> 01:27:08,096
蘇珊，我還是不明白我們來這兒幹什麼。
Susan, I still don't understand
why we're here.

1084
01:27:08,221 --> 01:27:10,511
信我吧，加裡。你會驚喜萬分的。
Trust me, Gar.
You're in for a real surprise.

1085
01:27:10,641 --> 01:27:13,559
你的驚喜萬分已經讓我緊張了。
Your surprises are beginning
to make me nervous.

1086
01:27:13,686 --> 01:27:16,473
-她怎麼說？
-我們會驚喜萬分的。
- What'd she say?
- We're in for a real surprise.

1087
01:27:16,605 --> 01:27:19,060
我想我們在這兒看不到Tony Bennett。
I guess we're not gonna see
Tony Bennett here.

1088
01:27:19,191 --> 01:27:21,230
我應該叫警察跟著我們。
I'd settle for a police escort.

1089
01:27:21,359 --> 01:27:24,194
你怎麼能讓她穿上羅伯塔的夾克？
How could you let her wear
Roberta's jacket?

1090
01:27:24,320 --> 01:27:28,449
嘿，她沒衣服了，總得穿點什麼吧。
Hey, she's cold.
She's gotta wear something.

1091
01:27:28,574 --> 01:27:30,947
為什麼你不把你的指甲剪了？
(dummy) Why don't you
cut your fingernails?

1092
01:27:31,077 --> 01:27:33,366
我聽不見你在說啥…
I can't hear what you're saying...

1093
01:27:33,496 --> 01:27:35,536
摀住叫喊
(muffled shouting)

1094
01:27:40,045 --> 01:27:43,994
迪茲，如果她看到我們倆都在這兒，
她很可能又一走了之。
Dez, if she sees us both here,
she'll probably just split again.

1095
01:27:44,132 --> 01:27:46,171
那你回去吧。
You could go home.

1096
01:27:46,300 --> 01:27:49,254
我要看看他媽的陌生人是誰。
I wanna see who this fuckin' stranger is.

1097
01:27:56,352 --> 01:28:00,432
讓我猜。三倍龍舌蘭到天亮。
Let me guess. Triple tequila sunrise.

1098
01:28:00,564 --> 01:28:02,640
姜味汽水。
Ginger ale.

1099
01:28:05,443 --> 01:28:07,353
你是威士忌。
And you're the Scotch.

1100
01:28:07,487 --> 01:28:09,397
這是你的。
This must be yours.

1101
01:28:09,532 --> 01:28:11,570
朗姆酒和Tab。
Rum and Tab.

1102
01:28:16,121 --> 01:28:18,991
坐著別動，我去找找陌生人。
Sit tight. I'm gonna
go look for the stranger.

1103
01:28:19,958 --> 01:28:21,997
什麼陌生人？
What stranger?

1104
01:28:22,127 --> 01:28:25,293
-天，她可真迷人。
-一坨漂亮的屎罷了。
- God, she's gorgeous.
- Beauty feces.

1105
01:28:38,392 --> 01:28:39,887
她在那。
There she is.

1106
01:28:40,019 --> 01:28:43,305
-哪？
-就在那兒，和買煙女說話的那個。
- Where?
- Right there. Talking to the cigarette girl.

1107
01:28:43,439 --> 01:28:46,226
那不是蘇珊。我之前從沒見過那個女孩。
That's not Susan.
I never even seen that girl before.

1108
01:28:46,359 --> 01:28:48,980
迪茲，那是蘇珊。你認為我能搞錯嗎？
Dez, that's Susan.
Don't you think I should know?

1109
01:28:49,903 --> 01:28:53,320
那可能是蘇珊，但不是我的蘇珊。
That might be a Susan
but that's not my Susan.

1110
01:28:53,449 --> 01:28:57,031
-那是我的蘇珊。
-那麼在巴特利公園的女孩是誰？
- That's my Susan.
- Then who was the girl at Battery Park?

1111
01:29:13,092 --> 01:29:15,085
誰是陌生人？
So who's the stranger?

1112
01:29:15,220 --> 01:29:17,295
吉米！
Jimmy!

1113
01:29:17,430 --> 01:29:19,470
誰是陌生人？
Who's the stranger?

1114
01:29:19,599 --> 01:29:22,090
-說來話長。
-嗯啊。
- It's a long story.
- uh-huh.

1115
01:29:22,226 --> 01:29:24,350
你怎麼也不會知道她的。
You wouldn't know her anyway.

1116
01:29:24,479 --> 01:29:26,518
-她？
-是，她。
- Her?
- Yeah. Her.

1117
01:29:29,275 --> 01:29:31,945
過來，找個私人空間去說話。
Come on. We'll talk about it in private.

1118
01:29:34,656 --> 01:29:36,694
敲門
(knocking)

1119
01:29:36,824 --> 01:29:39,445
我們還有三分鐘上場。
We've got three minutes before curtain!

1120
01:29:39,576 --> 01:29:41,616
戴上你的假髮馬上出發。
Get your wig on and get out there!

1121
01:29:49,961 --> 01:29:51,954
我在想蘇珊會不會出事。
I wonder what happened to Susan.

1122
01:29:52,089 --> 01:29:54,330
看起來像是你丟了女友。
Looks like you lost your girlfriend.

1123
01:29:54,466 --> 01:29:56,792
嘿，賴瑞，我結婚了，懂嗎？
Hey, Larry! I'm married, all right?

1124
01:29:56,927 --> 01:29:59,215
-哦，得了吧。
-怎麼？
- Oh, please!
- What?

1125
01:29:59,346 --> 01:30:01,386
樂隊聲
(band plays fanfare)

1126
01:30:06,144 --> 01:30:08,765
晚上好，女士們先生們。
Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

1127
01:30:08,896 --> 01:30:12,182
歡迎來到魔術俱樂部，我是主持人，雷。
Welcome to the Magic Club.
I'm your host, Ray...

1128
01:30:13,735 --> 01:30:16,605
酒吧生，給我結帳吧。
Bartender...
Can I have the check, please?

1129
01:30:18,239 --> 01:30:21,109
有誰從女皇區出來的嗎？
Hey, is there anyone out here
from, uh... Queens?

1130
01:30:21,242 --> 01:30:23,733
你。好的。我自己是從正常人家的肚子裡出來的。
You. Well, I'm from
normal parents myself.

1131
01:30:23,869 --> 01:30:25,067
零星笑聲
(scattered laughter)

1132
01:30:25,204 --> 01:30:29,616
是這樣的，今晚我們給大家一個特別的待遇。
Anyway, we got a special treat
for you people this evening.

1133
01:30:29,750 --> 01:30:32,206
讓我介紹一下獨一無二的，舉世無雙的…
Introducing the one, the only...

1134
01:30:32,669 --> 01:30:34,709
蘇珊，快上來。
Susan, get up here!

1135
01:30:34,839 --> 01:30:38,124
…還有他可愛的助手，Davina…
...and his very lovely assistant, Davina...

1136
01:30:38,258 --> 01:30:41,544
…今夜女王，鼓掌吧。
...Queen of the Night! So let's hear it!

1137
01:30:52,523 --> 01:30:55,726
加裡，那是…
(Leslie) Gary... Is that...

1138
01:30:55,858 --> 01:30:58,350
不會吧。
It can't be.

1139
01:30:58,487 --> 01:31:01,322
我太喜歡了，真是好魔術啊。
I'm really enjoying this. It's a great trick.

1140
01:31:09,914 --> 01:31:11,706
蘇珊？
Susan?

1141
01:31:11,833 --> 01:31:14,787
-羅伯塔？
-我不敢相信。
- Roberta?
- I don't believe it.

1142
01:31:15,544 --> 01:31:18,331
-羅伯塔…
-加裡，坐下。
- Roberta...
- Gary, sit down.

1143
01:31:26,013 --> 01:31:28,504
呃，我在這兒呆會兒，謝謝。
uh... I think I'll be staying, thank you.

1144
01:31:28,640 --> 01:31:30,218
鼓
(drum roll)

1145
01:31:52,080 --> 01:31:54,997
煙，要煙嗎？
Cigars? Cigarettes?

1146
01:31:57,210 --> 01:31:59,451
她還是很有型的啊。
She's really got style in a way.

1147
01:31:59,587 --> 01:32:01,627
她很不錯啊，加裡。
She's good, Gary.

1148
01:32:03,258 --> 01:32:05,297
哦，對不起。
(Larry) Right. Sorry.

1149
01:32:28,032 --> 01:32:30,070
尖叫
(Roberta screams)

1150
01:32:43,379 --> 01:32:45,419
(screams)

1151
01:32:47,967 --> 01:32:49,794
